headline: HP, Pure Storage, Sinclair, Jabil, and Arlo Technologies Shares Plummet, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks fell in the afternoon session after President Trump threatened a 'massive increase in tariffs' on Chinese imports, reigniting fears of a renewed US-China trade war.
